name: jabil
title: Test Engineer
descriptions: During this experience, I worked on manufacturing projects for multiple larget tech companies, leading them from start to finish.
I pioneered the implementation of new test line monitoring software, combining and replacing previous logging, failure analysis, and reporting tools, reducing errors and operator workload.
On one project, I managed a test site, supervising a team of three operators, overseeing testing, debugging, and resolution of customer failures.

name: boba
title: Bobarista
descriptions: I worked part-time as a barista at a boba shop in Los Altos.
I was responsible for front and back of the house operations, keeping inventory and handling customers.
